'''Alleanza Securitas Esperia''', also known as '''Allsecures''', was an Italian [[insurance company]]. It was formed in Rome in 1933 by a [[merger]] of Alleanza & Unione Mediterranea with Securitas Esperia, a part of the [[Assicurazioni Generali]] group.{{r|julie|page=182}} In 1965 it was the thirtieth Italian insurance company by total [[insurance premium]]s.{{r|medio|page=52}} It was merged into the [[AXA]] group in 1998.{{r|rob|page=110}}

