The '''Augusta Bay''' is located on the east coast of [[Sicily]], [[Italy]], about 270 [[nautical mile|nm]] south-southeast of [[Naples]].<ref name=glose>[http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/facility/augusta-bay.htm Augusta Bay Port Facility ]</ref>
It is the location of the '''Augusta Bay Port Facility''' which supports the [[United States Sixth Fleet|Sixth Fleet]] of the [[US Navy]]. The facility is distributed among Porto Megarese, Porto Xifonio and Seno del Priolo.<ref name=glose/>
